headline: Conagra Brands Hits 46th 52 Week Low: Value Play or Value Trap?
summary: The beleaguered branded food company hit its 46th new 52-week low of the past 12 months on Tuesday. Its stock is now trading at a 10-year low. Yielding nearly 8%, it has to be a value play. Doesn't it?
